<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/593730-why-is-it-so-boring">why is it so boring?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_593730'><a id="like_count_community_question_593730" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/593730?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">8 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F93269.Earth_Abides">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/593730-why-is-it-so-boring">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/593730-why-is-it-so-boring">See all 12 answers</a>
</li>
