<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link368357" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=368357&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F340855-for-a-reader-who-enjoys-philosophical%2Fanswers%2F368357-i-found-earth-abides">flag</a>
